bin/
obj/
# artifacts/ is the dotnet publish output directory (Task 20). The
# directory itself is tracked (README + .gitignore live here) but
# the publish outputs (PeakCan.Host.exe, .pdb files) are ignored.
# The .gitignore in artifacts/ lists the specific filenames.
artifacts/*
!artifacts/.gitignore
!artifacts/README.md
*.user
*.suo
.vs/
.idea/
TestResults/
coverage/
*.log
# v1.2.11: ephemeral subagent-driven-development briefs / reports.
# Not part of the repo — local scratch for the SDD workflow.
.sdd/

# Session-local artifacts (v1.5.0 ship cleanup):
# - .claude/agent-memory/ = pkm-capture agent working dir (transient)
# - .claude/vault-tmp/, vault-ttmp/ = vault-pkm temp dirs (transient)
# - .claude/transcript_tail.jsonl = session scratch (transient)
# - .claude/new_entry*.md = pkm-capture pre-format entries (transient)
# - docs/devlog.md = session work log, never committed (intentional)
# - mutate, release-lock, run-other-cleanup = 0-byte tool markers (transient)
.claude/agent-memory/
.claude/vault-tmp/
.claude/vault-ttmp/
.claude/transcript_tail.jsonl
.claude/new_entry.md
.claude/new_entry_v1_4_0.md
docs/devlog.md
mutate
release-lock
run-other-cleanup
